---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Kicker from "../components/Kicker.astro";
import Pullquote from "../components/Pullquote.astro";

// Sticky 目录
const sections = [
  { id: "what",    label: "Ⅰ · What this is",       label_zh: "这是什么" },
  { id: "why",     label: "Ⅱ · Why ≥ 3000 字",      label_zh: "为什么是长文" },
  { id: "two",     label: "Ⅲ · Two faces",          label_zh: "硬币两面" },
  { id: "name",    label: "Ⅳ · About the name",     label_zh: "关于 Coni" },
  { id: "author",  label: "Ⅴ · About the writer",   label_zh: "关于作者" },
  { id: "colophon",label: "Ⅵ · Colophon",           label_zh: "凡例" },
];
---

<Base
  title="About — conilab"
  description="Articles published twice — once in 中文, once in English. ≥ 3000 字 per piece. About the project, the name, and the writer."
>
  <section class="about">
    <div class="wrap about-grid">
      <!-- ── ASIDE: sticky TOC ── -->
      <aside class="about-aside" aria-label="Section index">
        <div class="aside-inner">
          <Kicker text="contents · 目录" />
          <ol class="toc">
            {sections.map((s) => (
              <li>
                <a href={`#${s.id}`}>
                  <span class="toc-en">{s.label}</span>
                  <span class="toc-zh cjk" lang="zh">{s.label_zh}</span>
                </a>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ol>
          <div class="aside-foot">
            <p class="aside-handle">
              <span class="cjk" lang="zh">@coni</span> ·
              <a href="https://github.com/coni555" rel="me">github</a> ·
              <a href="/articles/rss.xml">rss</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <!-- ── MAIN: bilingual longform ── -->
      <article class="about-main">
        <header class="about-head">
          <Kicker text="about · 关于" />
          <h1 class="about-title">
            An article <em>read twice</em>,<br />
            kept once.
          </h1>
          <p class="about-lede cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            每一篇<em>文章</em>都被写两次：一次中文，一次英文——
            不是翻译，是同一个想法在两种语言里各自降落一次。
          </p>
          <p class="about-lede-en" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            Each <em>article</em> is written twice — once in 中文, once in
            English. Not a translation: the same thought, landing in another
            tongue and growing slightly different roots.
          </p>
        </header>

        <!-- Ⅰ -->
        <section id="what" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅰ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">这是什么</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">What this is</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="prose cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            <p>
              <strong>conilab</strong> 是一份个人笔记本。这里的<em>文章</em>
              没有日更，没有热点——只发<em>三千字以上</em>、被认真打磨过的长文。
              短想法另在 <a href="/notes">/notes</a>。
            </p>
            <p>
              每篇文章都登记两次：一面中文，一面英文。两面都登记完，才算这枚硬币写完了。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="prose" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            <p>
              <strong>conilab</strong> is a personal notebook. Articles here
              earn their place by being <em>≥ 3000 字</em> and worked through
              with care — no daily posts, no trend-chasing.
              Quick takes live in <a href="/notes">/notes</a>.
            </p>
            <p>
              Each article is registered twice — one face in 中文, one in English.
              Both faces filed; only then is the coin considered written.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Ⅱ -->
        <section id="why" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅱ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">为什么是 ≥ 3000 字</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">Why ≥ 3000 字</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="prose cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            <p>
              短想法去别处。三千字是一道<em>诚意门槛</em>——它逼着我自己想清楚，
              而不是写出一段刚好够发朋友圈的金句然后假装那就是结论。
            </p>
            <p>
              不是越长越好。是写到三千字之前就该写完的话题，本来就没必要发。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="prose" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            <p>
              Shorter thoughts live elsewhere. The 3000-character bar is a
              <em>friction threshold</em>. It forces me to actually think a
              thing through, instead of crafting one quotable line and
              pretending that's the conclusion.
            </p>
            <p>
              Length is not the goal. The point: any topic that closes itself
              before 3000 字 didn't need to be published in the first place.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <Pullquote
          zh="同一个想法只用母语写一遍——它还没完成。翻过来再写一遍，才是同一枚硬币的两面。"
          en="A thought written only in its native tongue isn't finished. Written again from the other side, it becomes both faces of the same coin."
        />

        <!-- Ⅲ -->
        <section id="two" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅲ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">硬币的两面</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">Two faces, one coin</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="prose cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            <p>
              中英不是翻译关系，是同一个核被两种语言土壤分别长一遍——
              落在中文里长出的形状，和落在英文里长出的形状，<em>会不一样</em>。
              那不是翻译失误，是双面叙事本来就该这样。
            </p>
            <p>
              所以读中文版，能读到一面；翻过来读英文版，能读到另一面。
              两面都读，才看见这枚硬币的全貌。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="prose" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            <p>
              The two languages are not a translation pair — they're the same
              core, planted in two different language soils, growing
              <em>slightly different</em> shapes. The differences are not
              translation drift; they're the whole point.
            </p>
            <p>
              Read the Chinese side and you see one face. Flip the coin, read
              the English side, and you see the other. Read both — and you
              actually see the whole coin.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Ⅳ -->
        <section id="name" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅳ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">关于"Coni"</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">About the name</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="prose cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            <p>
              <strong>Coni</strong> 来自 <em>coin</em>，硬币——把最后两个字母
              <i lang="en">i</i> 和 <i lang="en">n</i> 调换位置就是 coni。
              名字本身就是一次<em>翻面</em>动作：<code>c-o-i-n</code> 翻过来，<code>c-o-n-i</code>。
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>conilab</strong> = coni + lab。把硬币的双面叙事
              做成一间小实验簿——所以章节用罗马数字 Ⅰ/Ⅱ/Ⅲ，所以图标是
              同心双圆 ⊙，所以你现在看的这一页本身就是实验的一部分。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="prose" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            <p>
              <strong>Coni</strong> comes from <em>coin</em> — swap the last
              two letters <i>i</i> and <i>n</i> and you get coni. The name
              itself is a small <em>flip</em>: <code>c-o-i-n</code> turned
              around becomes <code>c-o-n-i</code>.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>conilab</strong> = coni + lab. The two-faced coin,
              treated as a small experiment book — hence the Roman numerals
              Ⅰ/Ⅱ/Ⅲ for chapters, hence the concentric-circle ⊙ glyph,
              hence this page itself being part of the experiment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Ⅴ -->
        <section id="author" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅴ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">关于作者</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">About the writer</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="prose cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            <p>
              这里写下的，是一个网名：<strong>@coni</strong>。它来自 <em>coin</em>，硬币。
            </p>
            <p>
              硬币有两面，人也一样：一面<em>向内</em>，记录阅读、写作、情绪和自我修正；
              一面<em>向外</em>，探索 AI、工具、表达和创造的可能。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="prose" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            <p>
              All you'll find here is a handle: <strong>@coni</strong>.
              It comes from <em>coin</em> — a small object with two sides.
            </p>
            <p>
              A person also has more than one side: one turned <em>inward</em>,
              where reading, writing, emotions, and self-reflection happen;
              another turned <em>outward</em>, where AI, tools, expression,
              and creation begin.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Ⅵ -->
        <section id="colophon" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅵ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">凡例</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">Colophon</span>
          </h3>

          <dl class="colophon-list">
            <dt>Type</dt>
            <dd>
              <span class="cjk" lang="zh">英文：Source Serif 4 · Inter · JetBrains Mono</span><br />
              <span class="cjk" lang="zh">中文：Source Han Serif SC（思源宋体）→ PingFang SC fallback</span>
            </dd>

            <dt>Color</dt>
            <dd>
              OKLCH only. <em>正面</em> — accent-front <code>oklch(0.42 0.14 240)</code>.
              <em>反面</em> — accent-back <code>oklch(0.55 0.11 60)</code>.
            </dd>

            <dt>Stack</dt>
            <dd>
              Astro 6 · TypeScript strict · bun · Cloudflare Pages.
              No React, no Tailwind. Plain CSS, native components.
            </dd>

            <dt>Source</dt>
            <dd>
              <a href="https://github.com/coni555" rel="me">github.com/coni555</a> ·
              <a href="/articles/rss.xml">RSS</a> ·
              <a href="/sitemap-index.xml">sitemap</a>
            </dd>

            <dt>Built quietly</dt>
            <dd>
              <span class="cjk" lang="zh">没有 newsletter，没有评论区，没有点赞按钮。要回应这里的某个想法，请去你自己的笔记本里写一遍。</span>
              <br />
              <em>No newsletter, no comments, no like button. The way to respond to a thought here is to go write your own.</em>
            </dd>
          </dl>
        </section>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about { padding: var(--sp-44) 0 var(--sp-96); }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-72);
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--sp-32);
    }
  }

  /* ─── ASIDE ─── */
  .about-aside {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--sp-72) + var(--sp-22));
    align-self: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-aside { position: static; }
  }
  .aside-inner {
    border-top: 2px solid var(--accent-front);
    padding-top: var(--sp-18);
  }
  .toc {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: var(--sp-18) 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-12);
  }
  .toc a {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
    padding: var(--sp-4) 0;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    transition: color var(--dur-quick);
  }
  .toc a:hover { color: var(--accent-front-ink); }
  .toc-en {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-front);
  }
  .toc-zh {
    font-family: var(--cjk-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }

  .aside-foot {
    margin-top: var(--sp-32);
    padding-top: var(--sp-18);
    border-top: var(--sp-hairline) solid var(--rule);
  }
  .aside-handle {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .aside-handle a { color: var(--ink-2); }
  .aside-handle a:hover { color: var(--accent-front-ink); }

  /* ─── MAIN ─── */
  .about-main {
    max-width: 64ch;
  }

  .about-head {
    border-bottom: var(--sp-hairline) solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-32);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-44);
  }
  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(var(--fs-7xl), 4.4vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    margin: var(--sp-12) 0 var(--sp-22);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .about-title :global(em) {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
    color: var(--accent-back-ink);
  }
  .about-lede {
    font-family: var(--cjk-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    line-height: var(--lh-prose);
    color: var(--ink-2);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-12);
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
  }
  .about-lede :global(em) {
    font-style: normal;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-style: var(--cjk-em-line);
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent-front);
    text-decoration-thickness: var(--cjk-em-thickness);
    text-underline-offset: var(--cjk-em-offset);
  }
  .about-lede-en {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
    color: var(--ink-3);
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
  }

  /* ─── SECTION ─── */
  .about-sec {
    margin: var(--sp-44) 0;
    scroll-margin-top: var(--sp-96);
  }
  .sec-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-7xl);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--accent-front);
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-4);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .sec-h {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-22);
    border-bottom: var(--sp-hairline) solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-10);
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--sp-12);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .sec-h .cjk {
    font-family: var(--cjk-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-3xl);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .sec-h-en {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
    color: var(--accent-back-ink);
  }

  /* ─── PROSE ─── */
  .prose {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    line-height: var(--lh-prose);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .prose.cjk { font-family: var(--cjk-serif); }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 var(--sp-14); }
  .prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .prose strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: var(--fw-medium); }
  .prose em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent-back-ink);
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
  }
  .prose.cjk em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-style: var(--cjk-em-line);
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent-front);
    text-decoration-thickness: var(--cjk-em-thickness);
    text-underline-offset: var(--cjk-em-offset);
  }
  .prose a {
    color: var(--accent-front-ink);
    border-bottom: var(--sp-hairline) solid var(--accent-front);
  }
  .prose code {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.92em;
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--ink) 5%, var(--paper));
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  /* —— prose 段落上下间距：相邻 zh/en 段在 show-both 模式下用一道 hairline 分隔 —— */
  .prose + .prose {
    margin-top: var(--sp-14);
    padding-top: var(--sp-14);
    border-top: var(--sp-hairline) dashed var(--rule);
  }
  :global(html.show-zh) .prose + .prose,
  :global(html.show-en) .prose + .prose {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  /* ─── COLOPHON LIST ─── */
  .colophon-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-14) var(--sp-22);
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
  }
  .colophon-list dt {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    padding-top: 0.2em;
  }
  .colophon-list dd {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }
  .colophon-list code {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.92em;
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--ink) 5%, var(--paper));
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .colophon-list em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent-back-ink);
  }
  .colophon-list a {
    color: var(--accent-front-ink);
    border-bottom: var(--sp-hairline) solid var(--accent-front);
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .colophon-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--sp-4) 0; }
    .colophon-list dt { padding-top: var(--sp-8); }
  }
</style>
